  "text": "The dashboard JSON schema version migration pipeline has two parallel implementations:\n\n**Backend (Go):**\n- `apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/migrate.go` \u2014 The migration runner. Contains the `migrator` struct (singleton) with `Initialize()` (builds the migration map via `GetMigrations`) and `Migrate()` (the public entry point). The `migrate()` method applies frontend defaults, ensures unique panel IDs, then iterates from `inputVersion+1` to `targetVersion`, calling each registered migration function.\n- `apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/schemaversion/migrations.go` \u2014 The versioned migration function registry. `GetMigrations(dsInfoProvider)` returns a `map[int]SchemaVersionMigrationFunc` mapping version numbers 2\u201342 to their corresponding `V2`\u2013`V42` functions. Also defines `LATEST_VERSION = 42`, `MIN_VERSION = 0`, and helper types (`SchemaVersionMigrationFunc`, `DataSourceInfo`).\n- `apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/schemaversion/v2.go` through `v42.go` \u2014 Individual migration step files (41 files total, one per version). Each exports a function like `V2`, `V36`, etc. Some (V33, V36) are closures that accept a `DataSourceInfoProvider`.\n- `apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/frontend_defaults.go` \u2014 Applies DashboardModel/PanelModel constructor defaults to mirror frontend behavior before running migrations.\n- `apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/schemaversion/errors.go` \u2014 `MigrationError` and `MinimumVersionError` types.\n- `apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/schemaversion/migration_utils.go` \u2014 Shared utilities (GetStringValue, GetBoolValue, etc.).\n- `apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/schemaversion/datasource_utils.go` \u2014 Datasource migration utilities (GetDataSourceRef, MigrateDatasourceNameToRef, etc.).\n\n**Frontend (TypeScript):**\n- `public/app/features/dashboard/state/DashboardMigrator.ts` \u2014 The `DashboardMigrator` class with `updateSchema()` method that mirrors the backend logic. Contains `DASHBOARD_SCHEMA_VERSION = 42` and inline migration logic for all schema versions within a single large method using `if (oldVersion < N)` conditionals.",
